          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The headline feature is ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Prezi AI",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". This isn't a gimmick—it's a legitimate shift in how presentations get built.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's how it works: you type a topic or upload your content, and Prezi AI generates a full presentation in seconds. We're talking about structured slides, visual layouts, suggested talking points, and even imagery. The AI understands context, so if you're pitching a product, it doesn't just throw bullet points on a slide. It creates a narrative flow with visual hierarchy.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What I love about this approach:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Speed",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": A polished deck in under a minute. No more spending Sunday night aligning text boxes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Structure",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
