        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The analytics feature is underrated. Knowing which parts of your presentation someone lingered on—or skipped—tells you a lot about what resonates. Sales teams use this to qualify leads. Educators use it to spot topics that need reinforcement.",
