          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The learning curve is gentler than you'd expect. The canvas feels different from PowerPoint or Google Slides at first, but Prezi's interface guides you through frame connections and zoom paths. Within 30 minutes, most people are comfortable building their first presentation.",
