      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Don't over-zoom.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " The canvas is fun, but too much movement makes audiences dizzy. Use zoom intentionally—pull in for detail, pull out for context. Keep transitions purposeful.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Start with Prezi AI, then customize.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " The AI gives you a strong foundation, but your personal touch makes it yours. Swap in your brand colors, add your own images, and tweak the narrative flow.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use the video feature for async communication.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Recording a Prezi presentation and sharing the link is often more effective than scheduling another meeting. People can watch at their own pace and revisit specific sections.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Leverage analytics.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " After sharing a presentation, check who viewed it and where they spent time. This data is gold for sales follow-ups and content refinement.",
            "marks": []
