    "image_prompt": "Editorial tech thumbnail, 16:9. Incorporate the brand logo fetched from https://logo.clearbit.com/prezi.com as the clean focal element over a soft amber-to-cream gradient (Notion + Apple aesthetic). A presenter on stage pointing at a large screen showing a dynamic, zooming presentation with colorful connected nodes and visual storytelling elements floating in space. Glassmorphism cards, soft volumetric light, generous negative space for a title, no embedded text, no watermark. --ar 16:9 --style raw",
    "faq_items": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Prezi AI free to use?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Prezi AI is available on paid plans (Standard, Plus, and Premium). The free tier lets you explore basic Prezi features and templates, but the AI presentation generator requires a subscription. You can try it risk-free to see if it fits your workflow.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can Prezi replace PowerPoint for business presentations?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For many use cases, yes. Prezi excels at pitch decks, training sessions, and any presentation where storytelling matters. It's especially strong when you want to show relationships between ideas rather than linear slides. Some teams use both tools depending on the context, but Prezi handles most professional presentation needs.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How does Prezi Video work for remote meetings?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Prezi Video lets you appear on screen alongside your presentation content. Your visuals float, zoom, and animate around you as you talk. You can use it live in Zoom, Teams, or Google Meet, or record videos for async sharing. It looks significantly more polished than screen-sharing a slide deck.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
